dct_title_s: Expugnatio civitatis S. Augustini in America Sitae
dct_alternative_sm: Expvgnatio civitatis S. Avgvstini in America Sitae
dct_description_sm: Depicts Drake's raid on St. Augustine during his West Indian voyage of 1585-1586.
Shows fort, English fleet, boats, soldiers, buildings, vegetation, turtle.
From de Bry's Grand voyages, 1599 (Part XIII), plate 131.
